---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Market Analysis — InciKorea">
  <div class="container py-16">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">CLUNA Market Analysis & Positioning</h1>
    <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Strategic analysis of the UK K-beauty market and CLUNA's competitive positioning</p>

    <div style="max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.8;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;">Market Overview</h2>
      <p>The UK K-beauty market is experiencing 12-15% annual growth, driven by younger demographics (18-35) seeking ingredient-transparent, clinically-validated skincare. Korean brands have captured 18% of the premium beauty segment, with focus on innovation and natural ingredients.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;">CLUNA SWOT Analysis</h2>
      
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem 0; color: #0066cc;">Strengths</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <li>Proprietary ACC (Advanced Cooling Complex) technology</li>
        <li>Premium foil mask format aligns with UK trend toward single-use treatments</li>
        <li>Strong regulatory compliance & transparency narrative</li>
        <li>Korean heritage meets Western cosmetic standards</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem 0; color: #0066cc;">Weaknesses</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <li>Limited brand awareness in UK market</li>
        <li>Higher price point vs. mass-market alternatives</li>
        <li>New market entry requires significant distribution investment</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem 0; color: #0066cc;">Opportunities</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <li>Retail partnerships with Sephora, Space NK, Boots</li>
        <li>Direct-to-consumer via e-commerce</li>
        <li>Beauty subscription box placements</li>
        <li>Influencer partnerships in clean beauty space</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem 0; color: #0066cc;">Threats</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <li>Intense competition from Cosrx, Purito, Dr.Jart+</li>
        <li>Supply chain disruptions</li>
        <li>Regulatory changes in UK/EU cosmetics law</li>
        <li>Currency fluctuations (KRW/GBP)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;">Competitor Landscape</h2>
      <p><strong>Direct Competitors:</strong> COSRX (hydration focus), Purito (minimalist), Dr.Jart+ (clinical), Laneige (premium). Most position on efficacy and ingredient transparency, similar to CLUNA's pitch.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;">Go-to-Market Strategy</h2>
      <p><strong>Phase 1 (6 months):</strong> Build brand authority via content marketing (this site), partner with 2-3 premium retailers, launch direct DTC channel.</p>
      <p><strong>Phase 2 (12 months):</strong> Expand retail footprint, launch second product line, develop subscription model.</p>
      <p><strong>Phase 3 (24 months):</strong> Regional expansion (EU), clinical trials for innovation narrative, potential acquisition target for larger beauty groups.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
